Headquarters Regions: Greater New York Area, East Coast, Northeastern US
Full Description: We help users to invest in the stock market by forming groups. This can best minimize cost in purchasing stocks and the risk that comes with it. The user who forms the group (Group master) would set the buying price and invite other users to join his or her group. Invited members will see the set buying price and can choose to accept or reject the proposal made by the group master. If accepting the proposal, the user will be included inside the group. Once the market price matches the set buying price, the purchasing transaction will occur. Now the group will have to democratically vote to set the selling price. The logic for the set selling price will work the same as the set buying price.

Description: Mobile School Bus Tracking - first of its kind
Headquarters Regions: Greater New York Area, East Coast, Northeastern US
Full Description: More than 30 million kids travel by schoolbus everyday in the United States. Bus safety and whereabouts are big concerns for parents and school authorities. Mobile School Bus Tracking suit of apps are built to provide all the stakeholders (parents, kids, bus drivers and administrators) sense of security, real-time monitoring, easy of installation, and easy to use. Different editions of app suit different needs.  The basic app, the Driver Edition, provides the driver or bus operator the functionality to create a route and share it with parents on that route. The Parents Edition, priced at a very low monthly rate, provides real-time tracking functionality, on a map, for parents and alerts waiting parents at pickups and drop off  points. The Admin Edition is useful for the school authorities in efficfiently monitoring the movement of all buses on their routes. The Distributor Edition allows licensed distributors to conduct business over specified areas or regions (for outside USA).
